| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2899 — Recovery Inhibition (blacklock)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: bf3e28e8-6464-513c-bb9c-0f41aa2f1e86"
